{"tid":1301189,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[若要生活好，咪做哲學佬]如果你想讀哲學，可以入黎睇睇哲學會讀咩。","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T03:25:39.000Z","uid":128869,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4f76b5662d6e20b6dce37e785be3048a76f8d7e4","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"中大哲學系作為學界首個公開譴責林鄭政府暴力嘅學系，可能會有唔少後生仔想讀，我會嘗試解答一下哲學讀乜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Q:大學哲學係讀乜?</strong></span><br />\nA:大學哲學會必修哲學史，哲學即係古往今來重要嘅哲學家，你都要約略識下佢。仲會要求學生邏輯課成績唔可以太差。<br />\n然後你就可以揀選修嘅course，而course就會針對某一議題或流派，簡單黎講，即係會讀得比哲學史仔細。<br />\n有咩course，你可以上網搵到。<br />\n中大:<a href=\"http://www.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/web/zh-hant/courses/?academic-year%5B%5D=2018-2019&amp;wpv-course-type%5B%5D=phil-zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Fzh-hant%2Fcourses%2F%3Facademic-year%255B%255D%3D2018-2019%26wpv-course-type%255B%255D%3Dphil-zh-hant&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=1b092737\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/web/zh-hant/courses/?academic-year%5B%5D=2018-2019&amp;wpv-course-type%5B%5D=phil-zh-hant</a><br />\n港大:<a href=\"https://philosophy.hku.hk/dept/undergrad/courses-2019-20/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fdept%2Fundergrad%2Fcourses-2019-20%2F&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=1388b92f\" target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/dept/undergrad/courses-2019-20/</a><br />\n而我唔識浸大嘅宗哲，所以你可以去問浸大宗哲嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:大學哲學點上堂?</span></strong><br />\nA:一個哲學course就大約一星期三個鐘<br />\n通常會係兩個鐘lecture，即係個老師喺出面對面全個course嘅學生講書，你聽到有奇怪位可以challenge佢，然後佢就會令你覺得自己問得好蠢。<br />\n然後一個星期一個一個鐘嘅tutor/兩星期一個兩個鐘嘅tutor，即係個老師/助教帶住一個小組做group discussion，上tutor前要睇文，上tutor有機會要做presentation。唔睇文又唔識嘅話就會成程坐喺度。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:大學哲學有咩功課?</span></strong><br />\nA:主要係寫paper，少有少寫，多有多寫。可能係一學期中同尾交兩篇3000字嘅文，可能係一學期三篇2000字，係話唔埋的。<br />\n亦有可能係考試，但好少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Q:如果我想讀哲學，最好有咩特質? </strong></span><br />\nA:英文好/願意睇英文。基本上每個tutor都要睇文，而哲學唔理中哲定西哲，都有好多係英文，所以個個星期都要求你睇英文。<br />\n接受能力高。有啲哲學家講野同常人唔同，例如有啲唯心論主張呢個世界無客觀事物，一切都喺mind入面，你要有接納嘅心先有機會明佢講咩。同時接受自己有時/好多時會睇唔明哲學家up咩，接受自己嘅無知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:點解要喺大學讀哲學?</span></strong><br />\nA:接受比較正統嘅哲學訓練，你錯嘅時候有人指出。好多人去書局買本哲學書就以為自己識哲學，其實好易走火入魔。獨學而無友，則孤陋而寡聞。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:邊啲人適合讀哲學?</span></strong><br />\nA:有家底。如無，請用心考慮。哲學係眾科之母，同時都係乞食之母。讀哲學唔一定要主修。<br />\n<br />\n以下開放問題，得閒答。<br />\n我唔會祝各位都考得好成績，但我祝各位得到同自己努力成正比嘅成績。"},{"pid":"800892ee63b501b9d53da753a5a24e91d5934fc0","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed676eb51b5256f08efa8722a35f01aa467fbd5","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"以功利主義嚟講，我做阻爸係咪一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲囡囡一定會開心。"},{"pid":"ffda5f409ca81c697e52bca42c1468c34b2ec07a","tid":1301189,"uid":33088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"點睇LU Philo 同 Bu 宗哲<br />\n比你排呢四個ranking 你會點排"},{"pid":"045208afd044b338b7c32468bd6a2f14cfba2d07","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed676eb51b5256f08efa8722a35f01aa467fbd5","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"以功利主義嚟講，我做阻爸係咪一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲囡囡一定會開心。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:40:17.000Z","msg":"效益主義黎講，早睡早起身體好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c50c64d77cedd11e4bc012d4ff1cb482b5ed97","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ffda5f409ca81c697e52bca42c1468c34b2ec07a","tid":1301189,"uid":33088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"點睇LU Philo 同 Bu 宗哲<br />\n比你排呢四個ranking 你會點排"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:52:24.000Z","msg":"單論哲學高低 其實都唔需要排高低 讀undergrad課程 邊間嘅prof都足夠教得好 當然你可以去睇下唔同大學嘅老師名單 睇下佢地有無研究開你感興趣嘅topic<br />\n<br />\n不過好現實咁講 你間大學靚啲 你個學位都靚啲 <br />\n<br />\n於我而言 如果要主修哲學 最好唔好分心去宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6fa51f2f1598783515991264c583e82c83de3c","tid":1301189,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed676eb51b5256f08efa8722a35f01aa467fbd5","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"以功利主義嚟講，我做阻爸係咪一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲囡囡一定會開心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"你食到女<br />\n佢又玩得開心<br />\n<br />\n大家都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35220db1f8f7e2dbfb7b832c1da2eb96e4e6c946","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac6fa51f2f1598783515991264c583e82c83de3c","tid":1301189,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed676eb51b5256f08efa8722a35f01aa467fbd5","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"以功利主義嚟講，我做阻爸係咪一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲囡囡一定會開心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"你食到女<br />\n佢又玩得開心<br />\n<br />\n大家都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"艾牙gree with U牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa98b9a50a94733309eb42