n無所不包"},{"pid":"3719fe9ad4a1e16da4564be0a9025019673777e5","tid":1301189,"uid":208425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f22802d4cfaa9295d4b58cc67a9f61ed1e58690","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7acd259308b8fc682e423dac525d095e0b197e5f","tid":1301189,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fbbf04cb18de477516282ec7db60f5afe31404b","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"邊種機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"相機咋<br />\n我都想學我個frd咁飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   相機也好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"雖然哲學理論上係最冇性格定型嘅科，但係我真係睇到好多哲學人鍾意影相，例如我，又例如我果到個professor 玩到去幫New York Times影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩樣有關係嫁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 介唔介意我問就業，攝影點入行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（當然你都可以challenge冇性格定型果到，例如話根據MBTI之類性格測試，通常性格係introverted/ thinking)"},{"pid":"bf9e08c55cc83a181b29dbfd253d58df5ff39ff8","tid":1301189,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baec1895fe1acfe63f4fd3c67bd797cf34974d57","tid":1301189,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"你認唔認同 人人都可以幸福"},{"pid":"5749a98540083fdc1d0a5043c0114ff9dcf9cd7d","tid":1301189,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2678b919e02bfe48810d445e2eab54ae6b6ac9c","tid":1301189,"uid":208425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"sc